#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:124
msgid ""
"Returns a :ref:`KinematicCollision2D <class_KinematicCollision2D>`, which"
" contains information about a collision that occurred during the last "
":ref:`move_and_slide <class_KinematicBody2D_method_move_and_slide>` call."
" Since the body can collide several times in a single call to "
":ref:`move_and_slide <class_KinematicBody2D_method_move_and_slide>`, you "
"must specify the index of the collision in the range 0 to "
"(:ref:`get_slide_count <class_KinematicBody2D_method_get_slide_count>` - "
"1)."
msgstr ""
"返回一个 :ref:`KinematicCollision2D <class_KinematicCollision2D>`，它包含有关在上一次 "
":ref:`move_and_slide <class_KinematicBody2D_method_move_and_slide>` "
"调用期间，发生的碰撞的信息。由于物体在单个 :ref:`move_and_slide "
"<class_KinematicBody2D_method_move_and_slide>` "
"调用时，可能会碰撞多次，因此您必须在0到（:ref:`get_slide_count "
"<class_KinematicBody2D_method_get_slide_count>` - 1）的范围内，指定碰撞的索引。"

