#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:182
msgid ""
"Moves the body along a vector. If the body collides with another, it will"
" slide along the other body rather than stop immediately. If the other "
"body is a ``KinematicBody2D`` or :ref:`RigidBody2D <class_RigidBody2D>`, "
"it will also be affected by the motion of the other body. You can use "
"this to make moving or rotating platforms, or to make nodes push other "
"nodes."
msgstr ""
"沿向量移动物体。如果物体与另一个物体碰撞，它将沿着另一个物体滑动而不是立即停止。如果另一个物体是 ``KinematicBody2D`` 或 "
":ref:`RigidBody2D "
"<class_RigidBody2D>`，则它也会受到另一个物体的运动的影响。您可以使用它来制作移动的或旋转的平台，或使节点推动其他节点。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:184
msgid ""
"``linear_velocity`` is the velocity vector in pixels per second. Unlike "
"in :ref:`move_and_collide "
"<class_KinematicBody2D_method_move_and_collide>`, you should *not* "
"multiply it by ``delta`` — the physics engine handles applying the "
"velocity."
msgstr ""
"``linear_velocity`` 是以秒为单位的速度向量。与 :ref:`move_and_collide "
"<class_KinematicBody2D_method_move_and_collide>` 中的内容不同，您 *不应* 将其乘以 "
"``delta`` ——物理引擎会处理速度。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:186
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"``up_direction`` is the up direction, used to determine what is a wall "
"and what is a floor or a ceiling. If set to the default value of "
"``Vector2(0, 0)``, everything is considered a wall. This is useful for "
"topdown games."
msgstr ""
"``floor_normal`` 是向上方向，用于确定什么是墙，以及什么是地板或天花板。如果设置为默认值 ``Vector2(0, "
"0)``，则所有内容均视为墙。这对于自上而下的游戏很有用。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:188
msgid ""
"If ``stop_on_slope`` is ``true``, body will not slide on slopes when you "
"include gravity in ``linear_velocity`` and the body is standing still."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``stop_on_slope`` 为 ``true``，则当您在 ``linear_velocity`` "
"中包含重力并且物体静止不动时，物体将不会在斜坡上滑动。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:190
msgid ""
"If the body collides, it will change direction a maximum of "
"``max_slides`` times before it stops."
msgstr "如果物体碰撞，它将在停止之前最多改变 ``max_slides`` 次。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:192
msgid ""
"``floor_max_angle`` is the maximum angle (in radians) where a slope is "
"still considered a floor (or a ceiling), rather than a wall. The default "
"value equals 45 degrees."
msgstr "``floor_max_angle`` 是仍将坡度视为地板（或天花板）而不是墙壁的最大角度（以弧度为单位）。默认值等于45度。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:194
msgid ""
"If ``infinite_inertia`` is ``true``, body will be able to push "
":ref:`RigidBody2D <class_RigidBody2D>` nodes, but it won't also detect "
"any collisions with them. If ``false``, it will interact with "
":ref:`RigidBody2D <class_RigidBody2D>` nodes like with :ref:`StaticBody2D"
" <class_StaticBody2D>`."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``infinite_inertia`` 为 ``true``，则物体将能够推送 :ref:`RigidBody2D "
"<class_RigidBody2D>` 节点，但它也不会检测到与它们的任何碰撞。如果为 ``false``，它将与 "
":ref:`RigidBody2D <class_RigidBody2D>` 节点，就像与 :ref:`StaticBody2D "
"<class_StaticBody2D>` 一样交互。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:196
msgid ""
"Returns the ``linear_velocity`` vector, rotated and/or scaled if a slide "
"collision occurred. To get detailed information about collisions that "
"occurred, use :ref:`get_slide_collision "
"<class_KinematicBody2D_method_get_slide_collision>`."
msgstr ""
"返回 ``linear_velocity`` 向量，如果发生滑动碰撞，则旋转和/或缩放。要获取有关发生的碰撞的详细信息，请使用 "
":ref:`get_slide_collision "
"<class_KinematicBody2D_method_get_slide_collision>`。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:202
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
":ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` **move_and_slide_with_snap** **(** "
":ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` linear_velocity, :ref:`Vector2 "
"<class_Vector2>` snap, :ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` "
"up_direction=Vector2( 0, 0 ), :ref:`bool <class_bool>` "
"stop_on_slope=false, :ref:`int <class_int>` max_slides=4, :ref:`float "
"<class_float>` floor_max_angle=0.785398, :ref:`bool <class_bool>` "
"infinite_inertia=true **)**"
msgstr ""
":ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` **move_and_slide_with_snap** **(** "
":ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` linear_velocity, :ref:`Vector2 "
"<class_Vector2>` snap, :ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` "
"floor_normal=Vector2( 0, 0 ), :ref:`bool <class_bool>` "
"stop_on_slope=false, :ref:`int <class_int>` max_slides=4, :ref:`float "
"<class_float>` floor_max_angle=0.785398, :ref:`bool <class_bool>` "
"infinite_inertia=true **)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:204
msgid ""
"Moves the body while keeping it attached to slopes. Similar to "
":ref:`move_and_slide <class_KinematicBody2D_method_move_and_slide>`."
msgstr ""
"移动物体，同时使其保持附着在斜坡上。类似于 :ref:`move_and_slide "
"<class_KinematicBody2D_method_move_and_slide>`。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:206
msgid ""
"As long as the ``snap`` vector is in contact with the ground, the body "
"will remain attached to the surface. This means you must disable snap in "
"order to jump, for example. You can do this by setting ``snap`` to ``(0, "
"0)`` or by using :ref:`move_and_slide "
"<class_KinematicBody2D_method_move_and_slide>` instead."
msgstr ""
"只要 ``吸附（snap）`` 向量与地面接触，物体就会保持附着在表面上。例如，这意味着您必须禁用吸附才能跳转。您可以通过将 ``snap`` "
"设置为 ``(0, 0)``，或使用 :ref:`move_and_slide "
"<class_KinematicBody2D_method_move_and_slide>` 代替。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:212
msgid ""
":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **test_move** **(** :ref:`Transform2D "
"<class_Transform2D>` from, :ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` rel_vec, "
":ref:`bool <class_bool>` infinite_inertia=true **)**"
msgstr ""
":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **test_move** **(** :ref:`Transform2D "
"<class_Transform2D>` from, :ref:`Vector2 <class_Vector2>` rel_vec, "
":ref:`bool <class_bool>` infinite_inertia=true **)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_kinematicbody2d.rst:214
msgid ""
"Checks for collisions without moving the body. Virtually sets the node's "
"position, scale and rotation to that of the given :ref:`Transform2D "
"<class_Transform2D>`, then tries to move the body along the vector "
"``rel_vec``. Returns ``true`` if a collision would occur."
msgstr ""
"在不移动物体的情况下检查碰撞。实际上将节点的位置、比例和旋转设置为给定的 :ref:`Transform2D "
"<class_Transform2D>` 的位置、比例和旋转，然后尝试沿着向量 ``rel_vec`` 移动物体。如果发生冲突，则返回 "
"``true``。"

